summary: I've seen lots of people talking about the possibility of wooloo evolving into a 'wolf in sheep's clothing' type pokemon,  but...
body:
I’ve seen lots of people talking about the possibility of wooloo evolving into a ‘wolf in sheep’s clothing’ type pokemon, but I’ve been sitting here thinking about it evolving into something with the word 'loom’ (wooloom seems a little too similar but idk)

Of maybe a goat that knits with or uses its horns as a loom
